This Saturday, two of SA's greatest artists will be on stage at the State Theatre in Pretoria: rapper and songwriter Kwesta and award-winning multifaceted musician Sjava. The great news is that FIVE Sunday World readers can each win two tickets to attend this evening of electrifying music. Date: Saturday November 10 2018 Time: Performances start at 8pm Venue: South African State Theatre, Pretoria To enter the draw, email your full name, age and contact number to reader.competition@tisoblackstar.co.za before 8am on Friday November 9. PLEASE NOTE: Winners will have to collect their tickets in Parktown, Johannesburg, on Friday November 9 before 5pm after they have been notified.